text: Chicken scratch may refer to: * Chicken scratch or waila music of the Tohono O'odham people of Arizona and Northern Mexico * bird food, chicken feed * "Chicken scratch embroidery" is a form of cross-stitch embroidery done on gingham fabric, also known as "depression lace" or "snowflaking". * Chicken scratch guitar is a style of rhythm guitar playing associated with funk music. * Chicken scratching may also refer to penmanship that is very close to illegible.
title: Chicken scratch (disambiguation)
